						<p>A Fragment of a slab containing the images of the Saptamāṭṛkas, fixed into the South wall of the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>16th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This undated record can be assigned to 16th Century A.D. on palaeographical grounds.</p>						

